06:44:27.000Z","msg":"唔係冇拼搏精神<br />\n係依家大家都醒左<br />\n識得為我自己拼搏<br />\n而唔係咁on9幫班老闆拼搏"},{"pid":"c7fbf0eee8401c56d96ee87707d4212d8bdc6bef","tid":769180,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3891fd74e7299cbc72c7b18ea72b6e3601d8e4c3","tid":769180,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa20f55c0f3bcb4f7ccb9377e84de0fbd65b1c55","tid":769180,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f485eeff57f7ff022cd3b21b48f0b6e3558c8ca","tid":769180,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"有邊中學通識會教呢個金字塔？<br />\n智障就唔好衝出黎柒，廢柴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"好肯定中學有教<br />\n兩、三年前私補有見過<br />\n係教科書到有需求金字塔<br />\n好似係個人成長個個單元到<br />\n除非又改咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"個金字塔唔係講成長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"唉屌<br />\n好肯定有<br />\ndse前係喺中文課f6、7教<br />\ndse係喺ls教<br />\n我問下人搵唔搵到本ls書"},{"pid":"6b8d9c427fba3090f7f28c1db0a496698e1d5347","tid":769180,"uid":153031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68f779f7b6871b62d47efba80d3fcab9bf722aa6","tid":769180,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"政府用唔同嘅手段迫撚死香港人<br />\n香港人唔反抗就唯有揀返最有&ldquo;保障&rdquo;嘅政府工 冇樓又冇父幹而又要接受社會現實 只有政府工可以幫到你<br />\n<br />\n最後始終都揀係俾政府勞役 起碼政府唔似出面私人市場  淨係會壓搾你人工同假期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb197dde5687ba8d17dcfb59f77b50de28f8d7d2","tid":769180,"uid":153031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}